HEADWORD: Turbogenerator
<hw>Tur`bo*gen"er*a`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Turbine</er>, and <er>Generator</er>.]</ety> <def>An electric
generator or dynamo which is combined on one frame with a turbomotor, by
which it is driven.</def>⟦br⟧
